        1) JPQ: Java Persistence Query

        JPQ is ran based on Entity level, it interacts with JAVA Class and Object



        @Query Annotation for JPQL
            Positional vs Named Bind Parameters

                - Positional bind paratmer : ?1, ?2


                - Named Bind parameter: name must match --> : and @Param



        DDL Operation : add following annotation
        @ Modifying
        @Transactional


        Named Queries:
